thread.title: BARBARA GIESE

author: BARBARA GIESE
title: BARBARA GIESE
text: I have used ink farm 3 times now. I like the free shipping and promo code. this time however my cyan ( Red) was too full & leaked in my printer and the bottom of the printed paper. I did not tell the Ink Farm, Inc. about it because it was not leaking when I took it out of the package I had trouble pulling the tape off and that is when it started to leak.
